data.text: @RoyalReporter @SchuylerSistas_ This is damage limitation but nothing can undo the damage Harry has inflicted on the Monarchy . Harry is republicans greatest asset. The fact that politically motivated americans are all over your twitter says it all. @KensingtonRoyal  should be concerned.
@SchuylerSistas_ Knowing that what he did write about his father not being invited is false may make readers question the truth of other things in that letter.
@SchuylerSistas_ In my story in today’s paper I wrote that he had claimed his father was not invited but royal aides had indicated that both Meghan’s parents would be there.
@RoyalReporter Ah Patriarchy! But nice touch with her mother accompanying by car though..
